<p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2025年1月15日是遵义会议召开90周年纪念日。90年前，中国工农红军不畏艰险开启伟大的二万五千里长征，扭转了红军和中国革命的命运，形成了“坚定信念，坚持真理，独立自主，团结统一”的遵义会议精神。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;习近平总书记曾强调，“要运用好遵义会议历史经验，让遵义会议精神永放光芒。”一起学习↓</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20250211/1739239922573027185.png" title="1739239922573027185.png" alt="微信图片_20250210125927.png" width="658" height="1368" style="width: 658px; height: 1368px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20250211/1739240031477039927.png" title="1739240031477039927.png" alt="微信图片_20250210125932.png" width="656" height="1439" style="width: 656px; height: 1439px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20250211/1739240052482022084.png" title="1739240052482022084.png" alt="微信图片_20250210125935.png" width="662" height="1655" style="width: 662px; height: 1655px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20250211/1739240077176058404.png" title="1739240077176058404.png" alt="微信图片_20250210125938.png" width="659" height="1775" style="width: 659px; height: 1775px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20250211/1739240093216034980.png" title="1739240093216034980.png" alt="微信图片_20250210125941.png" width="659" height="1392" style="width: 659px; height: 1392px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20250211/1739240105300066295.png" title="1739240105300066295.png" alt="微信图片_20250210125945.png" width="650" height="1981" style="width: 650px; height: 1981px;"/></p>